OL,5,
OL,6,CG1966FThe pilot edition of How! airs
OL,7,Fon ITV (Southern region only).
OL,8,
OL,9,CG1967FThe final edition of At Last the
OL,10,F1948 Show airs on ITV.
OL,11,
OL,12,CG1971FSesame Street airs on ITV for
OL,13,Fthe first time (HTV region only).
OL,14,
OL,15,FThe programme would not be fully
OL,16,Fnetworked until 1986.
OL,17,
OL,18,CG1975FThe final episode of US series
OL,19,FThe Virginian: The Man from Shiloh airs
OL,20,Fon BBC One.
